flowRoot.flowPara: Liberating. The Guix System Distribution (GuixSD) is an advanced distribution of the GNU Operating System developed by the GNU Project—which respects the freedom of computer users.

Dependable. It comes with the GNU Guix package manager, which in addition to standard package management features, supports transactional upgrades and roll-backs, unprivileged package management, per-user profiles, and more.
Hackable. It provides Guile Scheme APIs, including high-level embedded domain-specific languages (EDSLs) to define packages and whole-system configurations.
